---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { weeklyEntries } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Weekly | lys Open Source System">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head page-intro">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Weekly</span>
        <h1>公开周更，不只是项目日志。</h1>
        <p>如果你想跟着这些项目一起学，这一页最有用。它告诉你最近真正推进了什么、现在能用到哪一步、下一步会补什么。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-grid">
      <article class="section-card">
        <h3>怎么看这页</h3>
        <p>把它当成公开学习日志，不必把每条都看成“项目管理记录”。重点是看哪些东西已经变成你可以上手、阅读和继续跟进的内容。</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="section-grid">
      {weeklyEntries.map((entry) => (
        <article class="weekly-card">
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="status-chip">{entry.date}</span>
          </div>
          <h3>{entry.title}</h3>
          <p>{entry.summary}</p>
          <p class="mono">Next: {entry.next}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
